question: What restaurant is available on the path leading to Alta Vista Gardens, Vista, CA from Sugarplum Zoo, Temecula, CA, within a radius of 160 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.055191 33.546915)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.219371 33.210166)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.055191 33.546915)',4326)::geography, 160000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-117.055191 33.546915)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
